1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:42,229
[I Don't Want to Be Friends With You]

3
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:51,000
[Everything About Li Jin Bu - Duan Xiao]

4
00:01:55,190 --> 00:01:56,560
[I'll use this diary]

5
00:01:56,650 --> 00:01:59,180
[to record every daily thing
between Li Jin Bu and me]

6
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:00,430
[starting from when we met.]

7
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:02,110
[If we get married someday,]

8
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,360
[it can be a souvenir.]

9
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:06,360
[December 24th, 1999.]

10
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:09,259
[This was the day we met.]

11
00:02:09,350 --> 00:02:11,060
[I met her in the bathhouse.]

12
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,380
[The details can't be written.]

13
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:14,310
[Then we had a fight
in my parents' hotel.]

14
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:17,390
[Her showing up
made me believe in so-called destiny.]

15
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:21,350
[May 1st, 2000.]

16
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,350
[She transferred to my school.]

17
00:02:23,790 --> 00:02:25,430
[We'll definitely get closer
to each other.]

18
00:02:25,990 --> 00:02:27,630
[May 1st, 2000.]

19
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:30,180
[We went to see the aurora on a holiday.]

20
00:02:30,270 --> 00:02:31,470
[It was exciting.]

21
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,470
[Thank God.]

22
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,280
[March 6th, 2001.]

23
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:39,380
[I don't know why she scolded me today.]

24
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:41,440
[I'm not in the mood to write.]

25
00:02:41,880 --> 00:02:44,120
[August 24th, 2001.]

26
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:46,230
[Soon, we'll go to college.]

27
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:47,340
[I have the confidence to say]

28
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:49,190
[that in the college]

29
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,390
[only one man can gain her heart.]

30
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,950
[And it should be me, Mr Duan.]

31
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,350
[My good days are coming.]

32
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,910
[I'm only one step away]

33
00:02:58,810 --> 00:03:05,430
[Episode 19]
[One Step Away]

34
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:30,910
You should drink less from now on.

35
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:32,200
It's bad for your health.

36
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:33,630
It's too late.

37
00:03:33,720 --> 00:03:34,840
You'd better go home.

38
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:38,440
I won't.

39
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:44,870
I have to review now.

40
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:47,000
If you stay here,
there's no way I can do it.

41
00:04:14,680 --> 00:04:15,670
I'm telling you, buddy.

42
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:18,200
I'm going to be a girl in my next life.

43
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,110
A pretty girl.

44
00:04:20,190 --> 00:04:23,230
I'm just going to sit here looking pretty
and wait for others to chase me.

45
00:04:23,320 --> 00:04:25,230
I won't be going after anyone.

46
00:04:25,320 --> 00:04:26,240
Good idea.

47
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,750
If this was before,

48
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:30,240
who would have believed
Chen Jun He could say so?

49
00:04:31,400 --> 00:04:32,280
Don't mention it.

50
00:04:34,950 --> 00:04:36,030
I understand.

51
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,080
We are all the same.

52
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:42,159
Look at me, I look like her guard.

53
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,300
If you were me, you wouldn't stand it.

54
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:47,030
But you made it, buddy. You made it.

55
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,670
Well, the good result

56
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,320
comes from the hard work.

57
00:04:50,790 --> 00:04:52,909
Like Xuan Zang in "Journey to West".

58
00:04:52,990 --> 00:04:54,240
To be honest,

59
00:04:54,950 --> 00:04:56,320
after succeeding in it,

60
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,710
I've felt a sense of emptiness.

61
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:01,640
Bro,

62
00:05:01,790 --> 00:05:03,230
can I ask you something?

63
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:05,600
Do you want to be beaten up now?

64
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:09,430
A sense of emptiness?
You're so fortunate.

65
00:05:09,520 --> 00:05:11,230
Trust me,

66
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:13,310
you will get it someday after you make it.

67
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,040
It looks like dating,

68
00:05:15,400 --> 00:05:16,750
but you need to be careful.

69
00:05:16,840 --> 00:05:18,600
You can't say the wrong thing.

70
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,440
Being buddies gives you freedom.

71
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:23,230
You're free to say whatever you want.

72
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:25,110
You're right. It's better to be buddies.

73
00:05:27,130 --> 00:05:27,310
[Waiting for You at the Four Seasons'...]

74
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:29,910
Listen,
you come back and break up with her now.

75
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:30,830
Right now.

76
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,520
And we bros enjoy ourselves together.

77
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:35,560
Do you think I don't dare to?

78
00:05:36,400 --> 00:05:37,280
Go!

79
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:43,360
Actually, I don't dare.

80
00:05:43,760 --> 00:05:45,080
What a freak.

81
00:05:46,670 --> 00:05:47,550
Let's go.

82
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,310
I started this trail.

83
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:55,950
I planted this tree.

84
00:05:56,030 --> 00:05:57,630
If you want go through the trail...

85
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,510
Wait a minute.

86
00:05:58,600 --> 00:05:59,480
Look at her,

87
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,750
doesn't she look familiar?

88
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:05,680
A little bit.

89
00:06:06,590 --> 00:06:07,470
Did you guys drink?

90
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:08,310
Do you want to join us?

91
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:10,430
Let's raise the glass together!

92
00:06:11,160 --> 00:06:12,870
It's so late. Hurry up and come home.

93
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,560
I won't.

94
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,910
My roommate said

95
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:19,350
that I'm about to be a student
at your college.

96
00:06:19,440 --> 00:06:20,190
I won't go.

97
00:06:20,280 --> 00:06:21,550
I'll stay with my buddy.

98
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,780
He... He won't go.

99
00:06:22,870 --> 00:06:24,870
Home is where a buddy is.

100
00:06:24,960 --> 00:06:26,830
He won't go home!

101
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:29,440
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

102
00:06:29,880 --> 00:06:32,190
Can't you two stop?
Aren't you embarrassed?

103
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,190
No.

104
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:34,190
I won't go anywhere!

105
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,430
I will stay with my bro.

106
00:06:35,520 --> 00:06:36,550
Right.

107
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:38,180
The two of us buddies

108
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:39,880
will never separate.

109
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:41,400
Don't...

110
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:42,400
Don't say nonsense.

111
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:44,470
Isn't there someone else?

112
00:06:44,550 --> 00:06:46,030
Don't forget about Hua.

113
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,470
We are three buddies.

114
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,990
Like in "Oath of the Peach Garden".

115
00:06:49,070 --> 00:06:49,950
Yes.

116
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:52,310
I'm Yun Chang then.

117
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:54,350
You are Yi De.

118
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,320
Yun Chang.

119
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:57,080
Yi De.

120
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,320
This...

121
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:06,550
Big brother!

122
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,430
Big brother?

123
00:07:09,870 --> 00:07:11,240
The big brother got angry.

124
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,560
Big brothers

125
00:07:12,760 --> 00:07:13,880
are all bad-tempered.

126
00:07:14,710 --> 00:07:15,550
Hey.

127
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,040
What are you guys doing here?

128
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,710
Isn't this our Zi Long?

129
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:23,920
Wait, Zi Long?

130
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:25,710
Zi Long.

131
00:07:26,590 --> 00:07:27,910
finally you're here.

132
00:07:28,000 --> 00:07:29,280
We were waiting for you!

133
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:32,040
What's wrong with the two of them?

134
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,270
Don't ask me.

135
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,710
I don't want to reason with them now.

136
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,670
Zi Long.

137
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,950
Have a drink with our big brother.

138
00:07:38,030 --> 00:07:39,140
Let's toast!

139
00:07:39,230 --> 00:07:40,110
Where's our wine?

140
00:07:40,350 --> 00:07:41,310
Fine.

141
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:42,430
Guys,

142
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:43,830
Big Brother is busy now.

143
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,240
Let's send the two of you home.

144
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,650
Go home.

145
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:49,840
Zi Long. Drink with our big brother.

146
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,920
Where are you going, Zi Long?

147
00:07:57,830 --> 00:07:58,880
Come, Zi Long.

148
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,230
Tell me, do you miss me?

149
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:04,520
Zi Long has to go home.

150
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:11,000
What a shame.

151
00:08:12,150 --> 00:08:13,030
Don't mention it.

152
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,440
Listen,

153
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,150
I'll stop drinking from now on.

154
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:18,190
I'll be mad at whoever asks me to drink.

155
00:08:20,710 --> 00:08:22,150
Now you know it's shame.

156
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,680
Yun Chang.

157
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:24,870
Yi De.

158
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:27,040
Why aren't you bowing to me,
your big brother?

159
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:29,830
We are big men.
Can we not bring up the past?

160
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,920
I'm not a man, I can bring up the past.

161
00:08:34,030 --> 00:08:35,000
So, buddies,

162
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:37,760
what were you doing yesterday?

163
00:08:41,039 --> 00:08:42,309
Don't look at me,

164
00:08:42,390 --> 00:08:43,870
wasn't it to comfort you?

165
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,910
Who asked you to comfort me?

166
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,200
Wasn't I encouraging you not to give up?

167
00:08:47,640 --> 00:08:49,430
You gave up after failing once.

168
00:08:49,990 --> 00:08:51,430
Be more ambitious.

169
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,400
Look at me.

170
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:55,590
My ambitions made me succeed.

171
00:08:58,470 --> 00:09:00,200
I'm thinking
whether I shall change my mind.

172
00:09:00,290 --> 00:09:01,190
Don't.

173
00:09:01,280 --> 00:09:03,310
You can't go back on your promise.

174
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:05,390
I'm leaving.

175
00:09:08,350 --> 00:09:09,430
Do you still want go after her?

176
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:11,040
Give us a definitive answer.

177
00:09:11,340 --> 00:09:12,400
It's just you.

178
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:13,840
Don't involve me.

179
00:09:14,560 --> 00:09:16,180
Some people are just hopeless.

180
00:09:16,270 --> 00:09:17,310
I can't help them anyway.

181
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:19,070
-Who are you talking about, brat?
-About you.

182
00:09:19,150 --> 00:09:20,120
Okay.

183
00:09:20,760 --> 00:09:21,640
Stop it.

184
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,150
Let's put the topic aside.

185
00:09:23,230 --> 00:09:24,200
Let's eat first.

186
00:09:32,910 --> 00:09:34,640
Hua, I don't want to eat
the steamed stuffed buns.

187
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,350
Can you give me two sandwiches?

188
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,430
-I don't have them.
-What?

189
00:09:38,510 --> 00:09:39,790
Of course you have them.

190
00:09:39,880 --> 00:09:41,510
If you don't give me any,

191
00:09:41,590 --> 00:09:42,840
I will die from hunger.

192
00:09:46,040 --> 00:09:47,540
Okay, tomorrow I'll make them for you.

193
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:48,630
Deal.

194
00:09:49,800 --> 00:09:50,680
I won't eat.

195
00:09:52,800 --> 00:09:54,320
Who cares.

196
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,720
Right...

197
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:57,360
Eat the buns.

198
00:10:01,190 --> 00:10:02,880
Wow, Li Jin Bu.

199
00:10:03,710 --> 00:10:05,880
You used to be cold and reserved.

200
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:07,670
You have changed in a blink.

201
00:10:08,110 --> 00:10:09,680
You've started cooking for him even.

202
00:10:09,990 --> 00:10:11,230
I'd have never expected it

203
00:10:11,310 --> 00:10:13,240
falling in love could turn you into this.

204
00:10:15,240 --> 00:10:17,230
This is really valuing a boyfriend
more than a friend.

205
00:10:17,640 --> 00:10:19,070
We've been together for so many years,

206
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:21,040
but you've never prepared any meal for me.

207
00:10:21,630 --> 00:10:23,000
Can you make one for me?

208
00:10:23,830 --> 00:10:24,920
Do it yourself.

209
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,230
Love is so terrifying.

210
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:33,240
Even a person like Lin Jin Bu
started cooking for a man.

211
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:37,350
I also want a boyfriend to cook for him.

212
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,720
I just want a boyfriend.

213
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:43,070
I have a gift for you.

214
00:10:43,160 --> 00:10:44,040
Me too.

215
00:10:44,680 --> 00:10:45,560
-What's that?
-What's that?

216
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:46,880
-You first.
-You first.

217
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:51,430
-We take it out together.
-Okay.

218
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:53,040
Three, two, one.

219
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,000
You can't sleep?

220
00:11:11,520 --> 00:11:12,520
We can have a chat.

221
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:21,480
I really don't know
how to help Wu Zhi Xun now.

222
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,950
Even if he has conflicts at home

223
00:11:24,030 --> 00:11:25,440
and he's in a bad mood,

224
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,600
it's not my fault.

225
00:11:28,280 --> 00:11:30,920
I worry about him
and take care of him every day.

226
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:33,830
But he's always pushing me away.

227
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,400
He even shouted at me yesterday.

228
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,350
Did he?

229
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:39,220
How dared he shout at you?

230
00:11:39,310 --> 00:11:40,190
It's not that.

231
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:42,350
I didn't want to leave his home,

232
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,710
so he raised his voice a bit.

233
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:45,560
This darn Four-Eyes got some skills...

234
00:11:46,030 --> 00:11:47,070
Don't look for him anymore.

235
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:48,320
How can you bear his anger?

236
00:11:49,110 --> 00:11:50,310
I can't do it.

237
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:52,080
Even his mother said

238
00:11:52,630 --> 00:11:54,070
that I'm his only friend.

239
00:11:54,160 --> 00:11:55,430
If I don't care about him,

240
00:11:55,510 --> 00:11:57,200
what do you think he can do?

241
00:12:00,350 --> 00:12:01,230
Whatever.

242
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:03,360
I can't control you.

243
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:05,630
It hurts me to see you like this.

244
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:33,910
What happened?

245
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:35,520
I'm a bit annoyed.

246
00:12:36,040 --> 00:12:37,280
Why?

247
00:12:38,950 --> 00:12:40,120
Because of Li Qing Tong.

248
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:44,190
Seeing her bearing Wu Zhi Xun's anger
every day

249
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,160
is upsetting.

250
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,550
Isn't this her own choice?

251
00:12:46,640 --> 00:12:47,550
Who can help her?

252
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:50,160
I used to bear your anger
every day before.

253
00:12:54,030 --> 00:12:55,230
But I liked it.

254
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:56,430
I wanted it.

255
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,990
But you also treat me very well.

256
00:12:58,800 --> 00:12:59,870
I think,

257
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,070
Wu Zhi Xun is not a good match.

258
00:13:01,800 --> 00:13:02,950
I realised it long ago.

259
00:13:03,270 --> 00:13:04,750
It's Chen Jun He's fault.

260
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,630
So useless.

261
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:06,670
What can he do except for fighting?

262
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:08,160
He can't be helped in any way.

263
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:16,080
Actually, I think we can still help.

264
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:20,080
You don't want to see
Li Qing Tong upset, right?

265
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:22,390
Even if Wu Zhi Xun doesn't like her,

266
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:23,950
someone else does.

267
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,040
Don't you reckon

268
00:13:26,590 --> 00:13:30,320
we should let Li Qing Tong experience
the sense of being loved?

269
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:31,470
Right?

270
00:13:31,550 --> 00:13:32,870
That's what friends do.

271
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,360
But what can we do?

272
00:13:34,950 --> 00:13:37,270
We can't make Li Qing Tong
like someone either.

273
00:13:42,230 --> 00:13:43,110
Leave it to me.

274
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:48,310
It's going to rain.

275
00:13:48,390 --> 00:13:49,270
Let's go.

276
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:00,150
Wu Zhi Xun.

277
00:14:00,920 --> 00:14:03,030
Can we have a talk?

278
00:14:19,000 --> 00:14:20,440
Stop drinking.

279
00:14:21,070 --> 00:14:22,270
I can't recognise you

280
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:24,560
acting like this now.

281
00:14:26,560 --> 00:14:27,550
What am I supposed to do?

282
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:30,150
I should live
the way you guys think, right?

283
00:14:30,240 --> 00:14:32,630
You can't mistreat yourself
like this either.

284
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:34,790
If you keep being like this, really...

285
00:14:34,880 --> 00:14:36,670
You'll really become a good-for-nothing.

286
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:38,200
I'm already a good-for-nothing.

287
00:14:38,720 --> 00:14:40,870
I can do nothing but study and take exams.

288
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,920
And now I can't even do that.

289
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:44,560
If I'm not useless, what am I?

290
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:55,000
If you can't stand it,

291
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:56,200
you can leave.

292
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:58,230
Don't come here anymore.

293
00:14:58,320 --> 00:15:00,440
I don't need you to show sympathy
and feel pity for me.

294
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:06,800
[Wu Zhi Xun.]

295
00:15:07,040 --> 00:15:08,430
[Why did you skip classes again?]

296
00:15:08,520 --> 00:15:10,240
[Your teacher called me.]

297
00:15:10,590 --> 00:15:11,950
[If you don't go again,
they'll expel you.]

298
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:13,430
And let them expel me then!

299
00:15:15,310 --> 00:15:17,390
Really, you can't act like this again.

300
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:19,270
If you don't study nor go to class,

301
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:21,350
what's the point
of repeating the year then?

302
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,880
Stop talking to me about that.

303
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:25,990
Stop drinking!

304
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:28,880
Did you count how many bottles of liquor
there are in your house?

305
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,320
Let it go.

306
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:31,760
No.

307
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:32,700
Let me go.

308
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:33,790
I won't.

309
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,630
Are you satisfied now?

310
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:41,270
You like smashing things
nowadays, don't you?

311
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:42,240
Yes.

312
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:43,990
Smash it then.

313
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,270
Just smash all these things.

314
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:46,640
I'll see how many you can smash.

315
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:48,680
That's all?

316
00:15:49,360 --> 00:15:50,240
Done?

317
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:11,040
You...

318
00:16:12,160 --> 00:16:12,950
Have you finished venting?

319
00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:14,200
Leave!

320
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,480
I won't.

321
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:23,960
What do you want to do?

322
00:16:24,280 --> 00:16:26,070
Do you want to watch me like my mum?

323
00:16:27,590 --> 00:16:28,470
Li Qing Tong,

324
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,600
I thought you were different from them.

325
00:16:31,400 --> 00:16:33,200
But I've realised you're like them now.

326
00:16:33,800 --> 00:16:35,750
You all think I should live
as you guys expect me to.

327
00:16:36,360 --> 00:16:38,270
But I want to be myself.

328
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:39,950
I've never played games

329
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:42,630
nor watched cartoons.
I've never drunk nor cursed at someone.

330
00:16:42,720 --> 00:16:44,660
But now I want to do all of that.

331
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:46,720
I want to do it happily.

332
00:16:47,800 --> 00:16:48,710
You won't leave?

333
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:50,360
Stay here then.

334
00:16:50,710 --> 00:16:52,950
Keeping cleaning,
washing clothes and cooking.

335
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:54,110
Up to you.

336
00:16:54,200 --> 00:16:55,590
You want to be with me?

337
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:56,870
Then do as you please.

338
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,190
I don't care.

339
00:16:58,280 --> 00:17:00,440
I'm an uncaring good-for-nothing anyway.

340
00:17:34,830 --> 00:17:35,710
Jin Bu.

341
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:37,320
Senior.

342
00:17:37,760 --> 00:17:39,040
You didn't bring your umbrella, right?

343
00:17:41,200 --> 00:17:42,080
Use mine.

344
00:17:43,750 --> 00:17:44,630
No need.

345
00:17:51,110 --> 00:17:52,200
You are...?

346
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:57,390
Can't you tell?

347
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,590
I...

348
00:18:04,680 --> 00:18:05,920
I won't disturb you.

349
00:18:11,910 --> 00:18:13,870
Why are you being so narrow-minded?

350
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:14,870
I am narrow-minded.

351
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:19,760
[I'm going to school.
Don't forget to eat something.]

352
00:19:36,950 --> 00:19:38,600
Where did you go last night?

353
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,280
Answer me.

354
00:19:45,110 --> 00:19:46,360
You went to visit Wu Zhi Xun again?

355
00:19:48,830 --> 00:19:50,040
You stayed there the whole night?

356
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:54,080
That's very good.

357
00:19:55,040 --> 00:19:56,110
But it's too early.

358
00:19:57,310 --> 00:19:58,400
What's early?

359
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:01,350
We got it.

360
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:03,520
Got what?

361
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:06,160
I've asked you something.

362
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:08,520
Li Qing Tong!

363
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:13,270
Early what?

364
00:20:13,880 --> 00:20:14,960
Getting up early.

365
00:20:17,640 --> 00:20:18,780
Really,

366
00:20:18,870 --> 00:20:20,510
I sat in his living room all night long

367
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:21,670
and did nothing.

368
00:20:21,750 --> 00:20:23,390
Then why didn't you come back?

369
00:20:23,680 --> 00:20:25,070
The rain was so heavy.

370
00:20:25,150 --> 00:20:26,220
And also, he didn't let me leave.

371
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:27,830
What could I do?

372
00:20:27,910 --> 00:20:29,520
He still knows to care about you.

373
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:34,680
Maybe there's no next time.

374
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:36,710
Why?

375
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:40,670
Is there anything going on with you two?

376
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:41,800
Tell me the truth.

377
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:47,190
What's wrong again?

378
00:20:47,270 --> 00:20:49,150
Can you leave me in peace for few days?

379
00:20:49,240 --> 00:20:50,120
I can.

380
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:52,590
As long as you're not afraid of
Li Qing Tong dating someone else,

381
00:20:52,670 --> 00:20:53,390
I'll leave you alone.

382
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:54,310
Stop kidding.

383
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:55,830
Who could she possibly date?

384
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:56,800
Wu Zhi Xun.

385
00:21:00,280 --> 00:21:01,910
You slapped him?

386
00:21:06,510 --> 00:21:08,040
No one could have let him
say those terrible things.

387
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:10,320
Besides,

388
00:21:10,560 --> 00:21:13,520
I really couldn't see him
give up on himself like that.

389
00:21:14,550 --> 00:21:15,630
Well done.

390
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:17,560
You don't have to always get
the cold shoulder.

391
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:21,830
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

392
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:23,030
Don't go there anymore.

393
00:21:23,120 --> 00:21:24,280
Stop bearing with his anger.

394
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:28,100
He's back again.

395
00:21:28,190 --> 00:21:29,630
He's repeating the year in Lin Yang.

396
00:21:29,720 --> 00:21:32,230
Li Qing Tong visits him at his place
every day.

397
00:21:32,320 --> 00:21:33,470
If you don't care,

398
00:21:33,560 --> 00:21:34,560
neither do I.

399
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:35,720
Wait.

400
00:21:38,840 --> 00:21:39,960
Explain me.

401
00:21:42,560 --> 00:21:43,830
Then tell me first.

402
00:21:43,920 --> 00:21:45,510
Do you still like Li Qing Tong?

403
00:21:45,590 --> 00:21:46,910
Of course.

404
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:47,590
Okay.

405
00:21:47,670 --> 00:21:49,600
Then do as I say.

406
00:21:50,600 --> 00:21:53,330
[Second Dining Hall] [Welcome]

407
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:55,270
Do you know what time it is?

408
00:21:55,360 --> 00:21:56,470
What time is it?

409
00:21:57,520 --> 00:22:00,360
It's time for our happiness to start.

410
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:05,830
Did you two get poisoned?

411
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:08,760
You get a happy cauliflower as a reward.

412
00:22:11,080 --> 00:22:12,070
Sorry.

413
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,040
Don't mind me.

414
00:22:13,360 --> 00:22:14,240
Go on.

415
00:22:19,720 --> 00:22:20,910
Li Qing Tong.

416
00:22:21,000 --> 00:22:23,190
Aren't you feeling very lonely now?

417
00:22:23,280 --> 00:22:24,310
Very lonesome?

418
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:26,760
Don't you want to feel the taste
of being loved

419
00:22:26,840 --> 00:22:28,600
and doted on by someone?

420
00:22:29,760 --> 00:22:31,520
Can you be nice?

421
00:22:33,790 --> 00:22:34,870
Right on time.

422
00:22:35,400 --> 00:22:37,400
Li Qing Tong is in need of someone's care.

423
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:41,520
Qing Tong.

424
00:22:42,320 --> 00:22:44,670
Do you know what time it is?

425
00:22:47,120 --> 00:22:49,390
It's time for your life to end.

426
00:22:49,480 --> 00:22:50,710
You're insane.

427
00:22:52,800 --> 00:22:53,680
No...

428
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:57,110
Why didn't it go according to the plan?

429
00:22:57,200 --> 00:23:00,720
Well, can you two learn
something different next time?

430
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:03,190
Nothing we can do...

431
00:23:03,400 --> 00:23:05,320
We have the same teacher.

432
00:23:05,740 --> 00:23:07,870
[F&A International Plaza]

433
00:23:13,560 --> 00:23:16,070
Why did we have to come here?

434
00:23:16,150 --> 00:23:16,250
It's so scary.

435
00:23:16,250 --> 00:23:17,400
[Come If You Dare]

436
00:23:17,400 --> 00:23:18,460
It's the trend recently.

437
00:23:18,550 --> 00:23:19,590
Very exciting.

438
00:23:19,670 --> 00:23:20,550
Yes.

439
00:23:22,120 --> 00:23:22,860
I won't play.

440
00:23:22,950 --> 00:23:23,830
I'm scared.

441
00:23:24,390 --> 00:23:25,500
Let's discuss about it.

442
00:23:25,590 --> 00:23:26,990
Discuss what? I won't play.

443
00:23:27,080 --> 00:23:28,950
I... I like that!

444
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:30,990
That's boring, it's for children.

445
00:23:31,080 --> 00:23:31,960
Let's play this.

446
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:33,600
Almost.

447
00:23:35,600 --> 00:23:36,480
Here he comes!

448
00:23:42,960 --> 00:23:43,840
Why he is here?

449
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:45,710
Right on time, he'll be your partner.

450
00:23:45,800 --> 00:23:46,430
Exactly.

451
00:23:46,510 --> 00:23:48,830
Aren't you always complaining
the two of us don't bring you along?

452
00:23:49,080 --> 00:23:49,790
We got you a partner.

453
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:50,760
Let's go!

454
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:52,320
No!

455
00:23:52,840 --> 00:23:53,960
Show her what you have.

456
00:23:57,080 --> 00:23:58,980
[F&A International Plaza]

457
00:24:01,560 --> 00:24:02,440
It's so scary.

458
00:24:03,990 --> 00:24:06,100
Didn't we exit too early?

459
00:24:06,190 --> 00:24:07,600
Should we go back to help?

460
00:24:07,840 --> 00:24:08,510
Not early at all.

461
00:24:08,600 --> 00:24:09,470
Li Qing Tong is timid

462
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:10,470
and afraid of the dark.

463
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:11,150
As we've come out,

464
00:24:11,240 --> 00:24:13,000
she can only hold onto Chen Jun He inside.

465
00:24:19,630 --> 00:24:21,270
Why weren't you scared just now?

466
00:24:21,520 --> 00:24:24,190
Even I felt scared in the darkest places.

467
00:24:24,280 --> 00:24:25,580
Really?

468
00:24:25,670 --> 00:24:26,550
Yi De,

469
00:24:26,640 --> 00:24:27,520
don't be scared.

470
00:24:27,640 --> 00:24:28,680
Your big brother will protect you.

471
00:24:28,920 --> 00:24:30,790
If I get a kiss,

472
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:32,160
I won't be scared.

473
00:24:32,760 --> 00:24:33,640
Stop it.

474
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:35,830
Xiao.

475
00:24:35,910 --> 00:24:36,870
Hurry up inside and look.

476
00:24:36,960 --> 00:24:37,920
Something happened.

477
00:24:42,760 --> 00:24:43,750
I'm so sorry.

478
00:24:43,830 --> 00:24:44,550
I'm really sorry.

479
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:46,510
There's something wrong
with my friend's brain.

480
00:24:46,590 --> 00:24:47,430
Normally it's not like that.

481
00:24:47,520 --> 00:24:48,190
Are you insane?

482
00:24:48,280 --> 00:24:50,750
Why can you fight wherever you go?

483
00:24:51,240 --> 00:24:52,120
Who told him to touch you.

484
00:24:52,360 --> 00:24:53,950
He's acting as a ghost!

485
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:56,360
It's his job!

486
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:57,560
I don't care.

487
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:59,440
I didn't hit him, I just pushed him a bit.

488
00:25:00,080 --> 00:25:01,480
Who told him to hit back?

489
00:25:02,550 --> 00:25:03,430
Fine.

490
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,830
He was worried about you.

491
00:25:08,840 --> 00:25:10,790
I can't interact
with such a violent person.

492
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:16,240
You asked me to protect her.

493
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,400
Why did Chen Jun He

494
00:25:30,800 --> 00:25:31,790
act like that?

495
00:25:32,120 --> 00:25:33,350
He ruined everything.

496
00:25:33,760 --> 00:25:35,270
I don't think it's a big problem.

497
00:25:35,360 --> 00:25:36,750
The girl scolded him,

498
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:40,560
but she won't hate
the person who protects her.

499
00:25:57,840 --> 00:25:59,240
Why... Why are you here?

500
00:25:59,750 --> 00:26:00,630
I'm sorry.

501
00:26:01,120 --> 00:26:02,200
It's all my fault.

502
00:26:02,830 --> 00:26:03,750
From now on,

503
00:26:03,830 --> 00:26:05,470
I will live properly.

504
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:06,990
I'll study hard for the university exam.

505
00:26:07,080 --> 00:26:08,870
I hope you won't be mad at me.

506
00:26:09,360 --> 00:26:11,190
Everything I said was out of anger.

507
00:26:11,280 --> 00:26:12,630
I didn't mean it.

508
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:15,200
If you're still willing to be my friend,

509
00:26:15,760 --> 00:26:17,350
I will prove you that with my actions.

510
00:26:20,230 --> 00:26:21,240
Thank you.

511
00:26:32,840 --> 00:26:34,950
Now it's really ruined.

512
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,670
Wu Zhi Xun showing up at this time

513
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:43,200
doesn't favour you.

514
00:26:48,080 --> 00:26:50,590
If things develop
according to the current situation,

515
00:26:52,230 --> 00:26:53,480
you won't stand a chance.

516
00:26:55,720 --> 00:26:58,560
Even I, such a master,
don't have any solution.

517
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:13,700
[Hello?]

518
00:27:13,790 --> 00:27:15,020
I'll meet you downstairs

519
00:27:15,110 --> 00:27:16,520
in five minutes.

520
00:27:18,280 --> 00:27:19,280
Where are you going?

521
00:27:35,360 --> 00:27:36,280
Li Qing Tong.

522
00:27:43,190 --> 00:27:45,320
What's that you couldn't say on the phone?

523
00:27:45,830 --> 00:27:47,400
Something I had to say in front of you.

524
00:27:51,360 --> 00:27:53,230
I don't know why I always mess with you.

525
00:27:53,310 --> 00:27:54,720
-But...
-I...

526
00:27:55,710 --> 00:27:57,030
I'm exhausted today.

527
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,390
I want to go back and sleep.

528
00:27:58,470 --> 00:27:59,910
-You can tell me tomorrow.
-Li Qing Tong.

529
00:28:01,110 --> 00:28:02,350
I'm not clever,
I don't know how to go after a girl.

530
00:28:02,430 --> 00:28:03,390
I've tried.

531
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,440
-But...
-Chen Jun He.

532
00:28:04,520 --> 00:28:05,600
Don't you have class tomorrow?

533
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:07,040
Go back and sleep.

534
00:28:07,760 --> 00:28:09,840
Li Qing Tong,
can you let me finish talking?

535
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:12,830
Are you crazy?

536
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:14,590
Why are you shouting
in the middle of the night?

537
00:28:14,680 --> 00:28:16,040
If you don't let me finish talking,

538
00:28:16,950 --> 00:28:18,680
we won't ever see each other again.

539
00:28:20,360 --> 00:28:21,320
That's fine.

540
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:25,240
Li Qing Tong.

541
00:28:30,200 --> 00:28:33,070
♫ The promise I didn't get to make ♫

542
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:36,430
♫ A story with an ending I can't admit ♫

543
00:28:36,520 --> 00:28:39,910
♫ Who knew you wanted to leave ♫

544
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:42,560
♫ The suffering of the fool ♫

545
00:28:43,400 --> 00:28:46,000
♫ How sad is it? ♫

546
00:28:46,760 --> 00:28:49,310
♫ A blank future ♫

547
00:28:49,400 --> 00:28:52,830
♫ A hand held up ♫

548
00:28:52,920 --> 00:28:56,230
♫ Shaking by itself in mid-air ♫

549
00:28:56,320 --> 00:29:00,390
♫ I gave it all to love you ♫

550
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:03,070
♫ A blank dream ♫

551
00:29:03,160 --> 00:29:06,510
♫ A hug that didn't happen ♫

552
00:29:06,590 --> 00:29:09,550
♫ No one responded to me to defend you ♫

553
00:29:09,640 --> 00:29:11,080
♫ My heart ♫

554
00:29:11,750 --> 00:29:13,240
♫ Is broken ♫

555
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:33,680
♫ All the hope and dreams are gone ♫

556
00:29:35,600 --> 00:29:40,320
♫ It's a joke to talk about
being reasonable and clear-minded ♫

557
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:44,840
♫ No one would understand ♫

558
00:29:45,600 --> 00:29:48,470
♫ The heaviness of having no answer ♫

559
00:29:48,560 --> 00:29:51,830
♫ A story with an ending I can't admit ♫

560
00:29:51,910 --> 00:29:55,310
♫ Who knew you had a reason
not to love me ♫

561
00:29:55,400 --> 00:29:57,960
♫ The suffering of the fool ♫

562
00:29:58,800 --> 00:30:01,390
♫ How sad is it? ♫

563
00:30:02,150 --> 00:30:04,710
♫ A blank future ♫

564
00:30:04,790 --> 00:30:08,230
♫ A hand held up ♫

565
00:30:08,310 --> 00:30:11,620
♫ Shaking by itself in mid-air ♫

566
00:30:11,710 --> 00:30:15,790
♫ I gave it all to love you ♫

567
00:30:15,880 --> 00:30:18,470
♫ A blank dream ♫

568
00:30:18,550 --> 00:30:21,910
♫ A hug that didn't happen ♫

569
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:24,950
♫ No one responded to me to defend you ♫

570
00:30:25,030 --> 00:30:27,920
♫ My heart is broken ♫

571
00:30:31,040 --> 00:30:32,560
I like you.

572
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:55,430
What did Chen Jun He

573
00:30:55,510 --> 00:30:57,000
tell you?

574
00:30:57,800 --> 00:30:58,680
Nothing.

575
00:30:59,880 --> 00:31:00,760
Well,

576
00:31:01,110 --> 00:31:02,360
how is it going

577
00:31:02,760 --> 00:31:04,120
between you two?

578
00:31:06,120 --> 00:31:07,800
Chen Jun He and I are no match.

579
00:31:11,160 --> 00:31:13,440
I know you wanted us
to be together in the past.

580
00:31:14,080 --> 00:31:16,470
But it's my own business.

581
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:19,160
I hope you can respect my choice.

582
00:31:25,320 --> 00:31:26,430
[Your business]

583
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:28,510
[is also mine.]

584
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:30,070
[If you can't be together,]

585
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:32,000
[what should I do?]

586
00:31:44,590 --> 00:31:45,520
Chen Jun He.

587
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:48,990
What's wrong?

588
00:31:50,720 --> 00:31:51,680
Let me go.

589
00:31:53,040 --> 00:31:54,270
Do you want to give up?

590
00:31:55,120 --> 00:31:55,910
It's none of your business.

591
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:57,280
Yes, it is.

592
00:31:57,720 --> 00:31:58,590
You don't have perseverance.

593
00:31:58,670 --> 00:31:59,550
But I do.

594
00:31:59,760 --> 00:32:01,160
You two can't just end like this.

595
00:32:01,560 --> 00:32:03,390
Can you avoid messing around here?
I'm playing basketball.

596
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:04,360
Come back.

597
00:32:04,920 --> 00:32:06,520
First promise me
you'll keep going after her.

598
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:09,710
Our thing has nothing to do with you.

599
00:32:09,790 --> 00:32:11,030
Nothing to do with me?

600
00:32:11,110 --> 00:32:12,790
You guys break up as you please,

601
00:32:12,870 --> 00:32:14,360
what about the child?
The child is unwanted?

602
00:32:16,800 --> 00:32:17,870
Are you crazy?

603
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:18,750
What child?

604
00:32:18,840 --> 00:32:19,720
What child?

605
00:32:19,880 --> 00:32:20,870
There's no child.

606
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:21,780
There's no child.

607
00:32:21,870 --> 00:32:23,750
I was joking.

608
00:32:24,840 --> 00:32:25,720
Chen Jun He.

609
00:32:26,070 --> 00:32:26,950
Wait...

610
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:30,070
Do you want to shout
about the child again?

611
00:32:30,150 --> 00:32:31,270
No more shouting.

612
00:32:31,350 --> 00:32:33,710
I'm telling you, if today's thing happened
and you were a boy, I would...

613
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:35,040
Hit me?

614
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:37,120
You are lucky to be a girl.

615
00:32:41,680 --> 00:32:42,630
You bullied your wife in high school.

616
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,230
And you even want
to hit your daughter in college.

617
00:32:44,760 --> 00:32:45,870
What a man.

618
00:32:56,870 --> 00:32:57,540
Forget it.

619
00:32:57,630 --> 00:32:58,720
I can wash them by hand.

620
00:32:59,510 --> 00:33:00,390
No.

621
00:33:00,680 --> 00:33:02,710
Do you have a screwdriver or a wrench?

622
00:33:02,800 --> 00:33:03,680
What do you want to do?

623
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:05,350
To repair it.

624
00:33:05,440 --> 00:33:07,390
I'm an expert at repairing things.

625
00:33:07,480 --> 00:33:08,400
I got it from my father.

626
00:33:09,190 --> 00:33:11,070
Are you sure you want to fix
the washing machine?

627
00:33:12,120 --> 00:33:13,080
You don't believe me.

628
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:16,470
Go to review.

629
00:33:16,560 --> 00:33:17,670
It won't take too long.

630
00:33:43,360 --> 00:33:44,440
Let me do that.

631
00:33:45,120 --> 00:33:45,990
No.

632
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:47,320
You can't do this.

633
00:33:52,400 --> 00:33:53,280
It should be fine.

634
00:33:54,190 --> 00:33:55,310
I'll plug it in and try.

635
00:34:01,910 --> 00:34:02,790
Incredible no?

636
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:07,160
I'm going to wash my hands.

637
00:34:32,920 --> 00:34:34,110
I have to stuff to do, I'm leaving.

638
00:34:34,199 --> 00:34:35,469
I will visit you next time.

639
00:34:36,110 --> 00:34:36,989
Thank you

640
00:34:37,670 --> 00:34:39,040
for repairing the washing machine.

641
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:44,270
Don't think about it.

642
00:34:44,760 --> 00:34:46,429
We've helped in any way we could.

643
00:34:46,520 --> 00:34:48,520
Let them solve the rest by themselves.

644
00:34:49,870 --> 00:34:51,860
When we get to the stop, just get off.

645
00:34:51,949 --> 00:34:53,350
Don't send me back anymore.

646
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:54,440
No way.

647
00:34:54,830 --> 00:34:56,560
I'll worry if I let you go back alone.

648
00:34:56,909 --> 00:34:58,920
It's safe in the daytime.

649
00:35:01,840 --> 00:35:02,750
You see,

650
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:03,800
I told you.

651
00:35:04,070 --> 00:35:05,390
It's dangerous in the daytime too.

652
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:14,390
[Time passes by day by day]

653
00:35:14,480 --> 00:35:16,710
[Li Qing Tong keeps not caring
about anything.]

654
00:35:17,080 --> 00:35:20,230
[She throws all her thoughts
at Wu Zhi Xun]

655
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:23,480
Here you are.

656
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:26,190
You eat first.

657
00:35:31,470 --> 00:35:33,270
[The National College Entrance Examination
is approaching.]

658
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:35,800
[It's the biggest obstacle of his life.]

659
00:35:41,200 --> 00:35:42,240
I want the blue one.

660
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:43,630
Move back.

661
00:35:43,720 --> 00:35:45,750
[We are still the same.]

662
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:47,360
[We go to school or we don't.]

663
00:35:47,920 --> 00:35:49,390
[We are either happy or not.]

664
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,830
[Times flies by]

665
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:54,280
[and make my anxiety dissolve slowly.]

666
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:01,510
[No matter if we have to part]

667
00:36:01,600 --> 00:36:03,150
[or if it's my destiny,]

668
00:36:03,240 --> 00:36:05,030
[I don't know how to solve any of it.]

669
00:36:05,120 --> 00:36:06,400
[So I don't think about it.]

670
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:10,630
It's for you.

671
00:36:10,720 --> 00:36:12,550
[Maybe there's still time.]

672
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:14,240
[Everything as a solution.]

673
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:37,380
Wu Zhi Xun.

674
00:36:37,470 --> 00:36:38,310
Good luck for tomorrow.

675
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:39,670
I believe you can do it!

676
00:36:40,760 --> 00:36:41,640
Thank you.

677
00:36:41,920 --> 00:36:43,040
Rest early.

678
00:36:43,840 --> 00:36:45,280
[You too. Good night.]

679
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:03,750
Hua.

680
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:04,750
The National College Entrance Examination
is over.

681
00:37:04,840 --> 00:37:06,230
Wu Zhi Xun wants to invite us
to a meal tonight.

682
00:37:06,310 --> 00:37:07,600
Ask Xiao to join us.

683
00:37:08,240 --> 00:37:09,640
Did you hear everything?

684
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:12,320
Bye.

685
00:37:15,220 --> 00:37:17,380
Which one do you think it's better
for tonight?

686
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:20,950
They're all good.

687
00:37:21,640 --> 00:37:22,520
It's up to you.

688
00:37:30,240 --> 00:37:31,030
Thank you Wu Zhi Xun

689
00:37:31,120 --> 00:37:33,150
for coming to our college
to treat us to a meal.

690
00:37:33,240 --> 00:37:34,550
And congratulations
for getting into a good university.

691
00:37:34,640 --> 00:37:35,680
Your college?

692
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:36,630
No.

693
00:37:36,720 --> 00:37:37,230
Their college.

694
00:37:37,320 --> 00:37:39,080
I come here so often that I'm used to it.

695
00:37:44,960 --> 00:37:45,910
Why do you look at me?

696
00:37:46,440 --> 00:37:47,510
I got invited by an old classmate.

697
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:48,600
How could I not come?

698
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:50,270
Xiao, the chopsticks please.

699
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:51,590
Of course you can come.

700
00:37:51,680 --> 00:37:52,560
Welcome.

701
00:37:54,160 --> 00:37:55,630
So how did the examination go this time?

702
00:37:55,710 --> 00:37:57,080
Do you need to repeat one more year?

703
00:37:58,600 --> 00:37:59,790
Shut up.

704
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:00,710
Rest assured.

705
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:01,720
I won't repeat it.

706
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:04,280
We have to celebrate then.

707
00:38:04,760 --> 00:38:05,830
Let's have a drink.

708
00:38:06,200 --> 00:38:07,080
Waiter.

709
00:38:07,270 --> 00:38:08,150
Chen Jun He.

710
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:10,080
What?

711
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:11,200
It doesn't matter.

712
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:12,720
Just drink a cup.

713
00:38:12,870 --> 00:38:13,750
There's no problem.

714
00:38:14,630 --> 00:38:16,190
He wants to drink.

715
00:38:16,280 --> 00:38:17,600
It has nothing to do with me.

716
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,150
Waiter,

717
00:38:19,240 --> 00:38:20,120
bring us a box.

718
00:38:25,840 --> 00:38:26,800
Stop drinking.

719
00:38:27,190 --> 00:38:28,880
Why are you drinking so much?

720
00:38:29,480 --> 00:38:30,360
I'm fine.

721
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:32,830
There's none left.

722
00:38:32,910 --> 00:38:34,430
I'll go buy two more.

723
00:38:36,040 --> 00:38:36,920
I'll go with him.

724
00:38:41,320 --> 00:38:43,400
Happy to watch the exciting scene?

725
00:38:44,350 --> 00:38:45,390
What could I do?

726
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:46,800
None of you cared about me.

727
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:57,230
[Open]

728
00:38:57,230 --> 00:38:58,110
Wu Zhi Xun.

729
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:02,040
What's wrong?

730
00:39:03,390 --> 00:39:04,630
Wow.

731
00:39:04,710 --> 00:39:06,790
Your Dongbei accent came out
after drinking a bit.

732
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:14,150
Do you have any feeling for Li Qing Tong?

733
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,870
It has nothing to do with you.

734
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:17,830
I know,

735
00:39:17,910 --> 00:39:18,960
but I want to ask.

736
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:24,320
Since it's none of your business,

737
00:39:24,760 --> 00:39:25,950
why would you ask?

738
00:39:28,880 --> 00:39:30,670
Although Li Qing Tong is inside,

739
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,110
I dare not touch you.

740
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:34,240
Think...

741
00:39:34,680 --> 00:39:36,270
I've known you for so long,

742
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:38,640
but I've never feared you
for even a second.

743
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:49,640
Take off your glasses.

744
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:51,160
It's convenient.

745
00:39:53,640 --> 00:39:54,960
What are you two doing?

746
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:57,630
Dreaming of going back
to No. 3 Middle School's playground?

747
00:39:58,040 --> 00:39:58,830
You've grown up.

748
00:39:58,920 --> 00:39:59,990
The girls are inside.

749
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:01,840
Don't embarrass yourselves.

750
00:40:09,630 --> 00:40:10,510
Wu Zhi Xun

751
00:40:12,560 --> 00:40:13,760
I'm not planning to give up.

752
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,070
Buddy.

753
00:40:18,160 --> 00:40:19,910
Don't get nervous first or you'll lose.

754
00:40:20,000 --> 00:40:20,740
So what?

755
00:40:20,830 --> 00:40:21,870
I will just lose.

756
00:40:21,950 --> 00:40:22,920
I never win anyway.

757
00:40:24,120 --> 00:40:25,000
Take the beer.

758
00:40:26,550 --> 00:40:27,960
Why should I?

759
00:40:29,520 --> 00:40:31,390
Why did I get nosy?

760
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,030
Let's go.

761
00:40:44,120 --> 00:40:45,000
Let's go for Karaoke.

762
00:40:45,800 --> 00:40:46,820
I'm not going.

763
00:40:46,910 --> 00:40:47,790
You guys go.

764
00:40:49,230 --> 00:40:50,110
I'm not going either.

765
00:40:51,600 --> 00:40:53,000
Won't you come back to school?

766
00:40:54,510 --> 00:40:56,270
How does it feel to be the heroine?

767
00:40:58,760 --> 00:40:59,960
It's not that good.

768
00:41:01,640 --> 00:41:03,040
I'm going to see Wu Zhi Xun.

769
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:01,840
Li Qing Tong.

770
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:05,030
No matter what I will say,

771
00:42:07,000 --> 00:42:09,360
I hope you will listen to me
until I'm done.

772
00:42:13,360 --> 00:42:14,830
What do you want to tell me?

773
00:42:14,920 --> 00:42:16,800
You're making me nervous.
